## Configuration

### API Base URL

The API base URL is configured in `MauiProgram.cs`:

```csharp
// Debug mode (uses localhost)
#if DEBUG
    Microsoft.Maui.Devices.DeviceInfo.Platform == DevicePlatform.Android
        ? "http://10.0.2.2:3000"  // Android emulator
        : "http://localhost:3000" // iOS simulator
#else
    "https://api.example.com"    // Production
#endif
```

## Architecture

This app follows the MVVM (Model-View-ViewModel) pattern:

- **Models**: Data classes representing business entities
- **Views**: XAML pages defining the UI
- **ViewModels**: Classes containing presentation logic and state

### Mizu Runtime

The `MizuRuntime` class provides:

- HTTP client with automatic token handling
- Secure token storage using MAUI SecureStorage
- SSE (Server-Sent Events) streaming
- Device information for mobile headers

